Package com.alvarpq.GOTF.coreGame.units

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AbilityBearer
    This interface should be implemented by all units which has a triggered ability.
    AttackType
    This interface defines the different attack types a unit can have.
    MoveType
    This interface defines the different move types a unit can have.
    PresenceApplier
    This interface should be implemented by units which need to apply buffs and debuffs to units.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Ability
    The superclass of all abilities returned by getAbility in AbilityBearer
    AttackType.NoAttack
    An attack type which makes a unit unable to attack.
    AttackType.Normal
    The normal attack type.
    AttackType.Relentless
    An attack type which makes a unit continue attacking with it's remaining attack after destroying an enemy.
    MoveType.Immovable
    A move type which makes a unit unable to move.
    MoveType.NonAdjacent
    A move type which makes a unit only being able to move to non-adjacent tiles.
    MoveType.Normal
    The normal move type.
